,"text":"Sometimes the night is just nighttime, sometimes I just need sleep"},{"s":59.64,"e":66,"text":"Nothing's chasing me, I can let it be Clouds pass over, but they don't own me"},{"s":66.22,"e":74.16,"text":"I don't have to fight, every thought I see I breathe once, breathe twice, come back home to me"},{"s":74.16,"e":77.42,"text":"If my thoughts get loud, I won't bow down I turn the volume of the fear back down"},{"s":77.42,"e":80.76,"text":"I call a friend, drink some water slow Open the window, let the cold air flow"},{"s":80.76,"e":84.26,"text":"No need to solve the whole world tonight No need to prove every feeling right"},{"s":84.26,"e":87.76,"text":"I can rest, I can pause, I can stay Let the panic dissolve away"},{"s":88.36,"e":94.78,"text":"I am not trapped in the noise I still have my name in my voice"},{"s":94.98,"e":101.5,"text":"This moment is smaller than it seems I can't wake up from anxious dreams"},{"s":101.5,"e":107.76,"text":"Hand on chest, count three There is still a place for me"},{"s":107.98,"e":116.72,"text":"Hand on chest, count four I don't need to run anymore"},{"s":117.76,"e":124.3,"text":"Nothing's chasing me, I can let it be Clouds pass over, but they don't own me"},{"s":124.3,"e":132.5,"text":"I don't have to fight, every thought I see I breathe once, breathe twice, come back home to me"},{"s":133.5,"e":139.42,"text":"Breathe in slow, breathe out clean I'm right here, I'm not between"},{"s":139.54,"e":146.5,"text":"Feet on floor, eyes on light I am safe inside tonight"},{"s":167.88,"e":167.96,"text":"Thanks for watching!"}],"duration":168,"source":"whisper","generatedAt":"2026-05-22T02:32:11.929Z","model":"whisper-1"}